{"about_the_game":"Endless chaos reverberates throughout a world where the only constant is war.<br><br>In an effort to overcome the turmoil, the people decide to create a super-loli. But this white-haired, god-like entity has\u2026 a major case of social anxiety?!<br><br>She turns the once apocalyptic, barren world into a new one filled with races and civilizations previously known only from mythology and fairy tales, and grants the mysterious power of The Source to its inhabitants, including humans.<br><br>Voice of Belldona takes place in this fantastic world created by Cheryl and tells the story of her adventures after being unexpectedly awakened again.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/\u9577\u7248\u6478\u982d.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/Character.png?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>Play as the powerful Sourcerer Griza or the mighty Warrior Rinna. <br><br>Embark on an adventure, collecting resources, buffs, armies, weapons, and deadly skill cards, through a series of unique narrative missions. Two characters. Two completely different combat systems. Gorgeously rendered ultimate skill animations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/Risana.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/gif_1.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/Fighting_Style.png?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>Create a powerful character uniquely yours, using preset decks with different playing styles as well as the cards and buffs you collect during your adventures.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/cards.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Powerful_Enemies.png<br><br>Be prepared. Your enemies will be strong... very strong.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/boss\u653b\u64ca.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/OnTheSky.png?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>Mechanical raptors. Pegasus cavalry. Flesh-tearing Harpies. Gain air superiority with amazing flying units never before seen in a roguelike card game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/\u7a7a\u8ecd_\u653b\u64ca.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>Deploy powerful aerial units to dominate the skies and disrupt enemy lines.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/\u9f8d_\u653b\u64ca.gif?t=1734272701\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/extras/Lore.png?t=1734272701\" /><br><br>Encounter an enigmatic non-human redhead, a critically wounded imperial officer, a lizard nun\u2014yes, you read that right!\u2014, a mysterious goblin collector who never reveals his face... and many more. In Voice of Belldona, weave your own story interacting with unforgettable characters you meet along the way.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734272701","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/page.bg.jpg?t=1734272701","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223420/66f0a2c45277d8b45be30ba40921f9c800f85fea/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734272701","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass